data.value:
Weeble Management is a patented system built specifically to automate rental and return processes.You will gain real-time visibility of your car inventory, on-lot location tracking, flexible query tools to instantly display car/group/fleet status, real-time, automatic capture of accurate fuel level and mileage—at both car exit and return, and unique controls for lot process optimization.
1.Increasing fuel revenues and reducing fuel costs by tracking and collecting more precise fuel and mileage data ·2.Optimizing car return/processing speed for improved rental yield and customer service ·3.Improving visibility of open slots on the ready line-and directing resources to close those slots more rapidly-to maximize car availability and rental revenue ·4.Checkout and return processes are automated using electronic rental contracts
The system has many unique advantages for managing-and maximizing- the value of rental car fleets, including:
·1.Proven ability to handle the wireless communication for hundreds of cars without interference ·2.Proven ability to work in any model or make of car ·3.Ability to work in any rental site configuration (city lot, indoors, outdoors, shared, etc.) including the ability to adapt it functionality automatically on a site-by-site basis ·4.Future-proof ability to download new functionality wirelessly
